reviewText: Perhaps a little "sappy", but who cares!  At least it's not bloodNguts--and who pays attention to the story when Lee Horsley's on the screen!  (I think he's one of those actors that was sorely over-looked.  Check out tapes on one of his series, Hawkeye!)It's just a great scenery, nice story of horses & two people from different lifestyles.Most relaxing.
